            <h2>Palette</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Left Click - Choose Color</li>
                <li>Right Click - Edit Color</li>
            </ul>
            <h2>Hotkeys</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Pencil: <span class="keyboard-key">B</span> or <span class="keyboard-key">1</span></li>
